CookieCat: Just to make you aware of how this Game Mode is played. At the start, there is one player who is the "Red Thing" and only they are aware of it. Every night , they have the ability to recruit other players onto their team, and if at any point the Things have the same number of players are regular villagers -  then they win!

The village can test 2, or 1 players every day, to check if they are on the Thing team. (Thing players also can sway the discussion, voting to save themselves). If the village are successful in a test, a Thing player will be eliminated. If they accidentally test a 'Human', then nothing happens, and the test is wasted.
